---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Visa Sponsored Tech Jobs in Ireland | Software Engineering & More"
description: "Find visa-sponsored tech jobs in Ireland with relocation assistance. Browse software engineering, data science, and product roles in Dublin, Cork, Galway and more."
permalink: /jobs-in-ireland/
---

{% set country_name = "Ireland" %}
{% set country_flag = "🇮🇪" %}
{% set grouped = jobs | groupByCountry %}
{% set countryJobs = grouped["Ireland"] or [] %}

{% block structuredData %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{ site.url }}/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Jobs by Country", "item": "{{ site.url }}/jobs-by-country/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Ireland", "item": "{{ site.url }}/jobs-in-ireland/" }
  ]
}
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "CollectionPage",
  "name": "Visa Sponsored Tech Jobs in Ireland",
  "description": "Find {{ countryJobs | length }}+ visa-sponsored tech jobs in Ireland with relocation assistance.",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}/jobs-in-ireland/",
  "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "{{ site.name }}", "url": "{{ site.url }}" },
  "mainEntity": {
    "@type": "ItemList",
    "numberOfItems": {{ countryJobs | length }},
    "itemListElement": [
      {% for job in countryJobs | limit(10) %}
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": {{ loop.index }},
        "item": {
          "@type": "JobPosting",
          "title": "{{ job.position }}",
          "datePosted": "{{ job.post_date }}",
          "validThrough": "{{ job.post_date | validThrough }}",
          "description": "{{ job.position }} at {{ job.company }} in {{ job.location }}. Visa sponsorship and relocation assistance included.",
          "employmentType": "FULL_TIME",
          "hiringOrganization": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "{{ job.company }}",
            "logo": "{{ site.url }}{{ job.logo }}"
          },
          "jobLocation": {
            "@type": "Place",
            "address": {
              "@type": "PostalAddress",
              "streetAddress": "",
              "addressLocality": "{{ job.location | extractCity }}",
              "addressRegion": "{{ job.location | extractCity }}",
              "postalCode": "",
              "addressCountry": "IE"
            }
          },
          "url": "{{ job.description }}"
        }
      }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    ]
  }
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{# Hero #}
<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50 to-white dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-gray-950 py-12 md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
    <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-600 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Home</a>
      <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
      <a href="/jobs-by-country/" class="hover:text-brand-600 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Jobs by Country</a>
      <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium">Ireland</span>
    </nav>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
      <span class="text-5xl">{{ country_flag }}</span>
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">
          Tech Jobs in Ireland
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">
          {{ countryJobs | length }} visa-sponsored positions with relocation assistance
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-6">
      <span class="badge badge-visa">Visa Sponsorship</span>
      <span class="badge badge-reloc">Relocation Assistance</span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
        Dublin, Cork, Galway & more
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Job Listings #}
<section class="py-12">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
      <h2 class="section-heading">All Positions</h2>
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">{{ countryJobs | length }} jobs</span>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      {% for job in jobs %}
      {% if "Ireland" in job.location %}
      <div class="job-card">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start gap-4">
          <img src="{{ job.logo }}" alt="{{ job.company }}" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg object-cover shrink-0" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='/favicon/android-chrome-192x192.png'">
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">{{ job.position }}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2">{{ job.company }}</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">
                <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
                {{ job.location }}
              </span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">
                <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
                {{ job.post_date | timeAgo }}
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {% if job.reloc %}<span class="badge badge-reloc">{{ job.reloc }}</span>{% endif %}
              {% if job.visa %}<span class="badge badge-visa">{{ job.visa }}</span>{% endif %}
              <span class="badge badge-contract">{{ job.contract }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="{{ job.description }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="job-card-apply">
            Apply <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 ml-1.5"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# SEO Content #}
<section class="py-12 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900/50">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Working in Ireland as a Tech Professional</h2>
    <p>
      Ireland is the European headquarters for many of the world's largest tech companies. Google, Meta, Apple, Microsoft, Salesforce, and Stripe all have significant operations in Dublin, making it one of Europe's premier tech hubs. The country's favorable corporate tax environment, English-speaking workforce, and EU membership create a unique ecosystem for tech professionals looking to advance their careers.
    </p>
    <p>
      The <strong>Critical Skills Employment Permit</strong> is Ireland's fast-track work permit for in-demand occupations, including most tech roles. It offers immediate eligibility for family reunification and a path to permanent residency after just two years. The <strong>General Employment Permit</strong> is another option for roles not on the critical skills list. Ireland's immigration process is employer-driven and generally efficient.
    </p>
    <p>
      Tech salaries in Ireland are competitive, typically ranging from €55,000–€90,000 for mid-to-senior engineers, with top companies offering significantly more. Dublin's cost of living, particularly housing, has risen substantially, but Cork, Galway, and Limerick offer more affordable alternatives with growing tech communities. Ireland's welcoming culture, vibrant social scene, and access to the EU make it an excellent base.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

